<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id7a35e63a-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id7a35e63b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section is comprised of <ref href="/us/pl/118/234/s112">section 112 of Pub. L. 118–234</ref>. Subsec. (c) of <ref href="/us/pl/118/234/s112">section 112 of Pub. L. 118–234</ref> amended <ref href="/us/usc/t54/s200103">section 200103 of Title 54</ref>, National Park Service and Related Programs.</p>
</note>
</notes>
